The paper discusses the use of Twitter data for electoral prediction, which falls under the categories of social media analysis (cs.SI), data mining (cs.SD), natural language processing (cs.CL), computational social science (cs.CY), and computational economics (cs.CE). The paper covers aspects such as data collection, processing, and performance evaluation, which are common in these sub-categories. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.SI and cs.SD, followed by cs.CL, cs.CY, and cs.CE.
